      "options": {
        "content": "**This dashboard covers everything ligate-api can serve today (`api.ligate.io`).**\n\n**VM-level metrics live on the sibling [`Ligate VM \u2014 Host metrics`](/d/ligate-vm) dashboard** \u2014 CPU, memory, disk I/O, network throughput, systemd unit status, ligate-node process stats. Sourced from `node_exporter` via Grafana Cloud Agent pushing to `grafanacloud-ligate-prom`.\n\n**Chain-runtime metrics (mempool depth, RPC latency by endpoint, DA submission failure breakdown, attestation rejection reasons) are still pending.** They require Prometheus scraping the chain's `127.0.0.1:9100/metrics` endpoint inside the VM. Tracked in:\n- [ligate-chain#316](https://github.com/ligate-io/ligate-chain/issues/316) \u2014 Ops deploy punchlist\n- [ligate-chain#360](https://github.com/ligate-io/ligate-chain/issues/360) \u2014 Pre-mainnet security gap tracker\n\nOnce that scraper lands, the existing chain-side dashboard at `ops/grafana/ligate-node.json` re-imports as a third dashboard alongside this one + the VM one.",
